node.text:
Directing the Finale of @cwsupermanandlois means I’ve now had the pleasure of directing both @tylerhoechlin and @grantgust and as such have come to the following conclusion:

They’re both very fast. 

#SupermanandLois

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tom Cavanagh on July 01, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
“it was a story where not only Scooter and the Big Man busted the City in half, but we kicked ass and remade the City, shaping it into the kind of place where our friendship would not be such an anomaly. And that...that is what I’m gonna miss. The chance to renew that vow and double down on that story on a nightly basis because...that is the thing we did together...the two of us.
How big was the Big Man? Too big to die. And that’s just the facts. You can put it on his gravestone, you can tattoo it over your heart. He doesn’t leave the E-Street Band when he dies. He leaves when we die”
 -Bruce Springsteen 

#mfa
 📷: @jannanni 

 🇨🇦Day
@theguyfromthemeeting
